{"tid":586450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【又一個月入群pm我】高登討論區將於Telegram上開Focus Group","createTime":"2018-03-09T13:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T03:45:27.000Z","uid":31219,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"25f7673b9fa85a62a51c0e48a541cc2ae53c9f91","tid":586450,"uid":31219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T13:48:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>此Focus Group立意有三：<br />\n<br />\n一﹑予部分會員率先試用高登討論區不同平台之新功能<br />\n二﹑有效收集意見並作出改善<br />\n三﹑加強討論區及網民互動關係<br />\n<br />\n有意入group者可於Telegram上搜尋gwangung1991，並回答以下三條問題：<br />\n<br />\n．帳戶名稱<br />\n．為什麼你想加入Focus Group<br />\n．你認為高登討論區有甚麼地方要改善<br />\n<br />\n開拓Telegram此渠道除方便收集意見，亦可更方便去處理會員帳戶問題。<br />\n<br />\n以下三點僅代表高登管理團向各位巴打絲打承諾：<br />\n<br />\n1. 關於帳戶解封﹑驗證或申請新帳戶時遇到問題，只要TG gwangung1991，一定會盡快跟進<br />\n<br />\n2. 關於高登重大事項改動，部分項目本公關會預先開放予部分會員試用（例如早前試新app），亦有部分項目會擬定問卷作廣泛咨詢，希望令會員感受到高登討論區的決心和愛<br />\n<br />\n3. 改善封鎖帳戶及刪帖制度，如涉及法律問題﹑刻意貼bam圖自爆或因其他問題「屢勸不改」等則會盡快處理。高登討論區冀望可為本地言論自由作出微薄貢獻，日後發展仍有賴各位會員支持及監察。<br />\n<br />\n以上<br />\n<br />\n再次感激每一位入來此post並讀畢全文的巴打絲打<br />\n<br />\nThanks all</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=BW&amp;message=6871371&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DBW%26message%3D6871371%26highlight_id%3D0%26page%3D1%26authorOnly%3DFalse&d=cPUuASb54NjB%2BpfASYGOkW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=2cdef70f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=BW&amp;message=6871371&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False</a>"},{"pid":"e6ee8c95a5a8538b35d11b55d6d9519485c084e3","tid":586450,"uid":31219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T13:51:57.000Z","msg":"有冇人入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06fc295002d991f45caee8e56551bb785281ecbb","tid":586450,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T1